<section class="about-intro" id="about">
  <div class="about-intro-text">
    <p class="section-label">What is Tesserae Bureau?</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">An unprecedented<br><em>boutique</em> model</h2>
    <p>Tesserae Bureau is a <strong>"boutique"</strong> law firm that breaks traditional market paradigms by providing custom-made legal services tailored to each client, through constant advisory and accompaniment, in areas strategically designed to guarantee greater efficiency and reach in the Ecuadorian and international markets.</p>
    <p>The firm was created to serve the needs of public and private entities, leveraging our partners' experience in both sectors. For those investing in Ecuador, Tesserae is particularly compelling: <em>"we know the world from the other side of the table."</em></p>
    <p>Our boutique model means we handle only selected matters in specific areas of law, guaranteeing specialized depth rather than superficial breadth. We are not a generalist firm.</p>
    <a href="/en/practice-areas/" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:1rem; display:inline-block;">View Practice Areas</a>
  </div>
  <div class="about-img">
    <img src="https://tesseraebureau.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Paola-Home-1.jpg"
      alt="Tesserae Bureau Partners" loading="lazy">
    <div class="about-img-caption">"We know the world from the other side of the table."</div>
