</section>

<section class="dark-section" id="philosophy">
  <p class="section-label">Our Philosophy</p>
  <h2 class="section-title">What guides<br>our <em>practice</em></h2>
  <p style="max-width:60ch; font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.9; color:rgba(237,233,224,0.6); margin-bottom:4rem;">
    <em>"All glory comes from daring to begin."</em> — Eugene Ware
  </p>
  <div class="values-grid">
    <div class="value-item" data-reveal>
      <p class="value-num">01</p>
      <h3 class="value-title">Absolute Rigor</h3>
      <p class="value-text">Every matter is handled with meticulous attention to detail. We leave nothing to chance. Our processes are structured, documented, and tested against the highest standards.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-item" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">
      <p class="value-num">02</p>
      <h3 class="value-title">Specialized Depth</h3>
      <p class="value-text">We provide services only in areas where we have genuine expertise. Our boutique model is deliberately selective — because depth produces better results than breadth.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-item" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
      <p class="value-num">03</p>
      <h3 class="value-title">Client Flexibility</h3>
      <p class="value-text">Flexibility is part of our DNA. We customize every process, timeline, and fee structure to the client's reality — not the other way around.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-item" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
      <p class="value-num">04</p>
      <h3 class="value-title">International Perspective</h3>
      <p class="value-text">With presence and networks across Latin America, Europe, and North America, we bring a genuinely global view to every cross-border matter.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

