      <p class="section-label">The Name</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">What does<br><em>Tesserae Bureau</em> mean?</h2>
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.9; color:var(--charcoal-mid); margin-bottom:1.5rem;"><strong>Tesserae</strong> derives from the Latin "tessera," identifying a piece of iron and bronze. In ancient times it served as a password and mark of honor, representing a pact of friendship, agreement, and other commitments. For the founding partners, <em>"Tesserae implies the pact between themselves and the commitment to their clients."</em></p>
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.9; color:var(--charcoal-mid); margin-bottom:1.5rem;"><strong>Bureau</strong> identifies the nature of the business as a law firm.</p>
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.9; color:var(--charcoal-mid);"><strong>Boutique</strong> means a firm that provides specialized products. The firm innovates and distinguishes itself by providing services only in certain areas of law, rather than offering the broad general services of a large firm.</p>
